public java.util.Collection getPddResources()
Return a collection of names for the pdd resources or an empty collection if none are found. If the isBpelDeployment method returns true, there should be at least one name in this collection.

getWsddResource

public java.lang.String getWsddResource()
Return the name of the wsdd resource (for straight Axis deployment) or null if none is found. The isBpelDeployment method should return false if this method does not return null.
